text.tspan: Bethany is a rather peculiar ghost who has a bag for a
head. She never went anywhere without one in life,
and in death the bag has fused to her head and become
her face. She is quite shy, but very nice once you gain
her trust. She really likes to knit, sew, and create
gifts for everybody inside the mansion, whether or not
she trusts or has ever even talked to them. Isn't she
the sweetest thing? She's also an amazing listener.
Put the fries in the bag
